<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Pickup & Return Mudah | Balikinaja</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Balikinaja - Layanan pickup barang retur anti ribet. Kami jemput barangmu, antar ke ekspedisi, dan update status via WhatsApp!" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="Pickup & Return Mudah | Balikinaja"/>
  <meta property="og:description" content="Solusi mudah untuk retur barang ke marketplace, jemput barang dari rumah, antar ke ekspedisi favoritmu. #Balikinaja"/>
  <meta property="og:type" content="website"/>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script>
    // Smooth scroll for anchor links
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
        anchor.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
          e.preventDefault();
          document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
        });
      });
    });
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 via-white to-orange-100 text-gray-800 font-sans">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-300 via-white to-blue-300">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-100 via-blue-100 to-white opacity-40 z-0"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-orange-700 mb-6 drop-shadow-lg animate-pulse">
        Pickup & Return Barang <span class="text-blue-600">Tanpa Ribet</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-800 mb-8 font-medium">Solusi tercepat untuk retur barang ke seller maupun marketplace. Kami jemput, kami antar, kamu tenang!</p>
      <a href="#booking" class="bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 transition text-white font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded-full shadow-lg text-xl animate-bounce">
        Booking Sekarang
      </a>
      <!-- Tidak ada logo di sini -->
    </div>
    <style>
      .animate-float { animation: float 2.5s ease-in-out infinite; }
      @keyframes float {
        0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
        50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
      }
    </style>
  </section>

  <!-- Layanan Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white" id="layanan">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-10 text-blue-600">Kenapa Pilih <span class="text-orange-500">Balikinaja?</span></h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-orange-100 via-white to-blue-50 shadow-xl rounded-2xl p-8 hover:scale-105 transition">
          <svg class="mx-auto mb-4" width="48" height="48" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 48 48"><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="#F59E42"/><path d="M16 22v10a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V22" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M24 14v14" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-orange-700 text-center">Pickup Retur ke Rumah</h4>
          <p class="text-md text-center text-gray-600">Gak perlu keluar rumah, barang retur kami jemput langsung di depan pintumu.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-100 via-white to-orange-50 shadow-xl rounded-2xl p-8 hover:scale-105 transition">
          <svg class="mx-auto mb-4" width="48" height="48" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 48 48"><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="#3B82F6"/><path d="M14 34V22a2 2 0 012-2h16a2 2 0 012 2v12" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M24 14v14" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-blue-700 text-center">Antar ke Ekspedisi</h4>
          <p class="text-md text-center text-gray-600">Kami antarkan ke ekspedisi favoritmu seperti JNE, J&T, SiCepat, dll.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-orange-100 via-white to-blue-50 shadow-xl rounded-2xl p-8 hover:scale-105 transition">
          <svg class="mx-auto mb-4" width="48" height="48" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 48 48"><circle cx="24" cy="24" r="24" fill="#F59E42"/><path d="M32 16v16a2 2 0 01-2 2H18a2 2 0 01-2-2V16" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M24 22v14" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-orange-700 text-center">Update & Bukti Resi</h4>
          <p class="text-md text-center text-gray-600">Status pickup dan foto resi otomatis terkirim ke WhatsApp kamu.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimoni Section -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-blue-50" id="testimoni">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-600 mb-8">Apa Kata Mereka?</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-6">
          <p class="italic text-gray-700 mb-4">“Proses retur jadi super mudah, driver ramah dan update status cepat! Recommended banget.”</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-3">
            <span class="font-semibold text-orange-500">Budi S.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-6">
          <p class="italic text-gray-700 mb-4">“Gak perlu ke ekspedisi, semua diurusin! Barang retur diambil langsung di rumah.”</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-3">
            <span class="font-semibold text-blue-500">Putri L.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-6">
          <p class="italic text-gray-700 mb-4">“Sangat membantu untuk retur barang marketplace, proses cepat dan mudah!”</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-3">
            <span class="font-semibold text-orange-500">Andi W.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-6">
          <p class="italic text-gray-700 mb-4">“Pengalaman retur jadi menyenangkan. Admin responsif dan informatif!”</p>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-3">
            <span class="font-semibold text-blue-500">Siti M.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Booking Form Section -->
  <section id="booking" class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-blue-600 mb-8">Booking Pickup Barangmu</h2>
      <form class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl space-y-6">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Nama Lengkap" class="w-full p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:border-orange-500 focus:outline-none" required />
        <input type="tel" placeholder="Nomor WhatsApp" class="w-full p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:border-orange-500 focus:outline-none" required />
        <input type="text" placeholder="Alamat Pickup" class="w-full p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:border-orange-500 focus:outline-none" required />
        <textarea placeholder="Catatan (opsional)" class="w-full p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:border-orange-500 focus:outline-none"></textarea>
        <button type="submit" class="bg-orange-500 text-white w-full py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-orange-600 transition text-lg">Kirim Permintaan Pickup</button>
        <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Atau chat langsung: <a href="https://wa.me/62881025735077" class="text-orange-500 underline font-bold">WhatsApp Admin</a></p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-orange-50" id="faq">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6 text-center">FAQ</h3>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-orange-600">Q: Apakah bisa pickup di hari yang sama?</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700">A: Bisa! Tim kami akan mengatur jadwal pickup sesuai permintaanmu.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-orange-600">Q: Barang apa saja yang bisa di-retur?</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700">A: Semua barang marketplace dan toko online, selama sesuai syarat ekspedisi.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-orange-600">Q: Bagaimana status pengiriman?</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700">A: Kamu akan menerima update dan foto resi via WhatsApp segera setelah pengiriman.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 py-8 bg-white">
    &copy; 2025 Balikinaja. All rights reserved. | <a href="#layanan" class="text-orange-500 hover:underline">Layanan</a> | <a href="#faq" class="text-orange-500 hover:underline">FAQ</a>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
